parameters: \N<Happy-looking child> Swings are definitely the most fun!

\N<Sota's friend> I found a stag beetle earlier! Isn't it
cool!
\N<Calm child> Big brother, you seem unlucky.

\N<Muddy child> I'm going to work hard and learn how to do a
backflip!
Shall I start a conversation? (Souta's event will progress)
\N<Hinata Aki> Doing a backflip is so easy!
\N<Hinata Aki> How about this? It's easy, right!
\N<Hinata Aki> You can do it if you try!

\N<Hinata Aki> Hehe~ Well, you know~ I'm a genius at
teaching!

\N<Hinata Aki> Oh, it's Taro! I didn't realize you were
here.
\N<Hinata Aki> I was teaching Sota how to do a backflip~

<Hinata Aki> By the way, Taro couldn't do a backflip since
he was little, right?
\N<Sota> Oh~ Taro-niichan can't do it, huh?

\N<Sota> I could do it right away if I tried a little
harder.
<Hinata Aki> Ahaha~ I'm being talked about~
\N<Hinata Aki> Huh... It's not here either, huh~
\N<Hinata Aki> Taro~! Do you know where my phone is?
\N<Hinata Aki> I noticed that it was gone.
\N<Hinata Aki> I see... That's right, huh~...
\N<Hinata Aki> I don't have any idea...

\N<Hinata Aki> You took supplementary lessons in the
classroom, right~? And then you went to club activities,
right~?

\N<Hinata Aki> We played at the park last, so I think it's
somewhere among these three.

\N<Hinata Aki> It's okay, it's okay! Since I'm the one who
lost it, I'll be the one to look for it!
\N<Hinata Aki> Alrighty! I'll do my best to search for it~!!
\N<Hinata Aki> Huh... It's not here either, huh~
\N<Hinata Aki> Souta~!! Today, we're going to play a lot~!!

\N<Sota> ...But, wasn't it Hinata-neechan who wanted to go
stargazing?

\N<Hinata Aki> Ugh... I've already taken my supplementary
lessons!

\N<Hinata Aki> I thought we could play today since we don't
have club activities, but you're not being cute at all~

\N<Sota> Hmm, then is it okay if I stay over at Aki-
neechan's house today?

<Hinata Aki> ...Today? Hmm... It's fine, but I should check
with my mom just in case.

\N<Sota> If that's the case, it's fine! Aki-neechan's mom
said it's okay!
<Hinata Aki> Is that so? Since when...

\N<Hinata Aki> Then, how about playing soccer until it gets
dark? We haven't been able to do it together because of
studying for tests.
\N<Sota> I seriously got better, you know?
\N<Sota> I won't lose to Aki-neechan anymore!
\N<Hinata Aki> You've become quite cheeky, Sota!

\N<Hinata Aki> The difference in skill between me and Sota
is like the sun and a turtle!

\N<Sota> If you say that, Aki-neechan, then it's like the
moon and a turtle...
\N<Hinata Aki> S-Stop it! It's not that different!

\N<Hinata Aki> If you get too cheeky, I won't go easy on
you, you know?
\N Hinata Aki: Alright... then let's get started...
\N<Sota> Hey~ Aki-neechan, there's sand on your skirt.
\N<Sota> Hmm... I can't seem to get it right...
\N<Sota> I wish I could see it live~<K♥>
\N<Hinata Aki> Hmm... Did I get it?
\N<Sota> Hehe... <K♥> I got it, I got it! <K♥>
